{"tid":1354375,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小拿星！而家啲老師係咪癲架","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:45:00.000Z","uid":284589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"129f6ab448db64cd2808e19b6d4bee951951d32d","tid":1354375,"uid":284589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"睇到我火滾，有病唔好教書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要拎細路嚟出氣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1724123831234913/posts/2268554446791846/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1724123831234913%2Fposts%2F2268554446791846%2F&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQRFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=125599de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1724123831234913/posts/2268554446791846/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾個月前出過post講學生比老師迫害到創傷後遺症事件，書展開始，我就約左幾個雙職家長既學生去書展，因為爸爸媽媽根本都唔會有時間同佢地去到，係書展上撞到佢地既同學，其中一個就係之前我講個位學生，我見佢好開心係度睇書，有同學就同佢傾。<br />\n<br />\n傾傾下我先發現，佢地係學校比老師發脾氣既事，當時係五月尾，考試前仲有上外藉老師堂，老師一入課室就已經拎班長嚟發脾氣，又推同學落地，掉同學書包，佢地形容係暴龍一樣咁發癲同破壞，最後仲因為飛一張櫈去創傷後遺症同學後面張檯，令張檯反左壓住個個同學雙腳，之後個位同學唔知點樣比佢成功跑左落去搵社工，社工同副校上去就發現幾個受傷既同學，帶走佢地之後，個個同學就係校務處驚到係度大喊喊到收唔到聲。<br />\n<br />\n社工冇辦法控制先通知家長，小朋友話媽媽想叫白車，但社工同老師話唔好，最後媽媽同佢call的士去醫院，去到醫院，醫生睇完去叫警察嚟睇，同叫爸爸報警，社署之後都安排社工同小朋友做左遊戲治療。<br />\n<br />\n我聽完真係好心痛，點解而家既老師，情緒有問題仲可以教書，仲拎小朋友嚟出氣，我同媽媽傾，媽媽只有無奈，學校同佢傾，佢都話佢都冇話可說，根本只要老師話自己情緒有問題，學校都唔可以對佢做啲咩，只能夠叫小朋友自己執生，唔對路就跑去搵其他大人。<br />\n<br />\n老師有情緒病，根本就唔應該再比佢教書同接觸小朋友啦，家長根本冇辦法可以睇到佢有冇食藥，而家呢個教育制度仲要害幾多個小朋友，係咪要去到有大鑊野，老師發癲斬學生時，先至關注老師既質素同問題呢<br />\n<br />\n如果家長可以知道老師屬於那種情緒病，會更容易了解和處理，好可能老師因在病困中也未能自救，不要等到傷及小孩子身心靈才處理，已經太遲了⋯⋯"},{"pid":"52858a9811e5055a30a525bf24432e96c5b8a020","tid":1354375,"uid":284589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8899dbc8174b9ffd10a00876c644d9549ca045","tid":1354375,"uid":284589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562f671d9feb9a195b6a5438de0e051ae1f86338","tid":1354375,"uid":284589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7048faf31b2ea90f595c8840e00812cd56a0d1","tid":1354375,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"htt